body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.  
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of personal information.  
Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand.
The conversation should be at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time and end the conversation.
Return the conversation formatted like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Good morning! This is Billy Gonzales from the DreamHome Real Estate Agency. May I have your name, please?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Hi Billy, I'm Hannah King. I'm actually really excited to talk to you today.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: It's great to have you with us, Hannah! How can I assist you today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I have some concerns about privacy with my property listings. I just want to make sure my personal information is safe.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: I understand your concerns, Hannah. Ensuring your privacy is our top priority. Could I get your phone number and email address to verify your account?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Of course, my phone number is four one five - five five five - one two three four. And my email is hannah.king@example.com.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Hannah. I have verified your account. Now, let's address your concerns about privacy. We have strong measures in place to protect your personal information.

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: That sounds reassuring. I really appreciate your help with this.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: You're welcome! Is there anything else I can help you with today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: No, that's everything. Thank you so much, Billy.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: It was my pleasure, Hannah. Thank you for reaching out to DreamHome Real Estate Agency. Have a great day!
